explanation: The solution iterates through the word from right to left, adding characters to a StringBuilder. It stops when the length of the StringBuilder is equal to or greater than numFriends, and returns the substring from the start to numFriends. This approach ensures that the lexicographically largest string is found, as it considers the most significant characters first.

